<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Ticket Received 🎉</title>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;700&display=swap');

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background-color: #2e0249;
            color: #f3e8ff;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 30px auto;
            padding: 25px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #570df8, #f87272);
            border-radius: 16px;
            color: #f3e8ff;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }

        .header {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-align: center;
            color: #ffedd5;
        }

        .content {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.8;
            margin: 20px 0;
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 12px;
        }

        .content ul {
            padding-left: 20px;
            list-style: none;
        }

        .content li::before {
            content: '🌟';
            margin-right: 8px;
        }

        .content p {
            margin: 10px 0;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #ffedd5;
        }

        .footer a {
            color: #fde047;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .footer a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">🎫 Ticket Received! 🎉</div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hey <%= name %>,</p>
            <p>Thanks for trusting <strong>me</strong> (yes, that is me!) with your support needs. 😊</p>
            <p>Here's what you shared:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Message:</strong>
                    <%= ticket.message %>
                </li>
            </ul>
            <p>Don't worry, I (that is me again!) am already on it and will respond ASAP! 🚀</p>
            <p>Until then, why not check out more about me?</p>
            <p>Cheers, <br>That is me (again!) ✌️,<br><strong>ScammerPatil</strong></p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Made with ❤️ and a sprinkle of funk by ScammerPatil.</p>
            <p>Visit my portfolio: <a href="https://scammerpatil.vercel.app/">ScammerPatil</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>